01>
we do not need JUnit dependency so we have removed it
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
02>
we need TestNG dependencies and selenium dependencies, so we will download them from - https://mvnrepository.com/
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
03>
search TestNG and collect the latest dependency for my case today on 5th july it was - 
<!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.testng/testng -->
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.testng</groupId>
    <artifactId>testng</artifactId>
    <version>7.10.2</version>
    <scope>test</scope>
</dependency>

add this in pom.xml and use CTRL+S to save the changes in pom.xml, automatically by using CTRL+S your pom.xml will be able to download the dependency from https://mvnrepository.com/ 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
04>
search "selenium java" and collect the latest dependency, for my case today on 5th july it was -

<!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.seleniumhq.selenium/selenium-java -->
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.seleniumhq.selenium</groupId>
    <artifactId>selenium-java</artifactId>
    <version>4.22.0</version>
</dependency>

add this in pom.xml and use CTRL+S to save the changes in pom.xml, automatically by using CTRL+S your pom.xml will be able to download the dependency from https://mvnrepository.com/ 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
05>
