    <artifactId>extentreports</artifactId>
    <version>5.1.1</version>
</dependency>

add this in pom.xml and use CTRL+S to save the changes in pom.xml, automatically by using CTRL+S your pom.xml will be able to download the dependency from https://mvnrepository.com/ 
